'''瑪格麗特·威爾'''（{{lang-en|Margaret Wille}}）是[[美國|美國]]政治人物和[[律師|律師]]，2012年至2016年間擔任代表第九選區的[[夏威夷郡|夏威夷郡]]議會議員。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Aloha Margaret Wille|url=https://www.westhawaiitoday.com/2016/12/07/north-hawaii-news/aloha-margaret-wille/|accessdate=2021-02-15|author=|date=2016-12-07|publisher=West Hawaii Today|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Candidate Q&A: Hawaii County Council — Margaret Wille|url=https://www.civilbeat.org/2016/07/candidate-qa-hawaii-county-council-margaret-wille/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2016-07-27|work=Honolulu Civil Beat|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201150943/https://www.civilbeat.org/2016/07/candidate-qa-hawaii-county-council-margaret-wille/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=VIDEO: Margaret Wille Delivers Scathing Rebuke Of Mayor Kenoi|url=https://www.bigislandvideonews.com/2016/11/09/video-margaret-wille-delivers-scathing-rebuke-of-mayor-kenoi/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2016-11-09|publisher=Big Island Video News|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021045731/http://www.bigislandvideonews.com/2016/11/09/video-margaret-wille-delivers-scathing-rebuke-of-mayor-kenoi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外曾擔任過夏威夷郡民主黨主席。

== 生平 ==
就讀[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]][[本寧頓學院|本寧頓學院]]文化人類學專業。後移居[[夏威夷島|夏威夷島]]<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=他孤獨地追求轉基因作物真相|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/health/20140120/t20gmo/zh-hant/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2014-01-20|publisher=紐約時報中文網|archive-date=2019-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191008013348/https://cn.nytimes.com/health/20140120/t20gmo/zh-hant/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年當選代表第九選區的夏威夷郡議會議員。

作為夏威夷郡議會農業委員會主席，威爾反對在夏威夷島上種植[[基因改造生物|基因改造]]作物，認為「這無異於放任他們（跨國公司）吞併我們的島嶼」<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Hundreds gather for Hawai'i Island proposed GMO bill ban hearing|url=https://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/22749195/hundreds-gather-for-hawaii-island-proposed-gmo-bill-ban-hearing/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2013-07-02|publisher=Hawaii News Now|language=en|archive-date=2013-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130804051014/http://www.hawaiinewsnow.com/story/22749195/hundreds-gather-for-hawaii-island-proposed-gmo-bill-ban-hearing|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年，威爾起草和提出第113號法案，目的是「禁止對基因改造農作物進行露天種植、繁殖、發展或測試」<ref>{{Cite web|title=528 Revolution Historic Anti-GMO Bill by Sherri kane and Leonard Horowitz Horokane|url=http://www.528revolution.com/historic-anti-gmo-bill-passed-paradise/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2013-10-17|publisher=528 Revolution|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227080921/http://www.528revolution.com/historic-anti-gmo-bill-passed-paradise/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該法案在11月獲郡議會通過，12月5日獲郡長{{le|比利·克諾伊|Billy Kenoi}}簽署<ref>{{Cite web|title=Mayor signs GMO bill 113 into law|url=https://www.bigislandvideonews.com/2013/12/05/mayor-signs-gmo-bill-113-into-law/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2013-12-05|publisher=Big Island Video News|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118050731/http://www.bigislandvideonews.com/2013/12/05/mayor-signs-gmo-bill-113-into-law/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年，威爾當選夏威夷郡民主黨主席<ref>{{Cite web|title=VIDEO: Wille New Hawaii County Democratic Party Chair|url=https://www.bigislandvideonews.com/2017/05/06/video-wille-new-hawaii-county-democratic-party-chair/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2017-05-06|publisher=Big Island Video News|language=en|archive-date=2017-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515040055/http://www.bigislandvideonews.com/2017/05/06/video-wille-new-hawaii-county-democratic-party-chair/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

她是[[伯尼·桑德斯|伯尼·桑德斯]]的支持者<ref>{{Cite web|title=Wille unopposed for county Dems top spot|url=https://www.hawaiitribune-herald.com/2017/04/18/hawaii-news/wille-unopposed-for-county-dems-top-spot/|accessdate=2021-02-15|date=2017-04-18|publisher=Hawaii Tribune-Herald|language=en-US}}</ref>。

